Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to hold her tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to be closer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.80,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.00,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I am such a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:01.40,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.40,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's not like I wanted to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she... still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she had to leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.60,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,She won't even give me a chance to apologize, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.90,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,No, maybe there isn't even a need for that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:20.70,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If I just disappear from her life, won't that solve everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.70,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.30,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Siblings can't just say they love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.00,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Saying that you love your sibling like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.40,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.00,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I know that it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I got a bit ahead of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.60,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,"What do you think of me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.60,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have asked such a shameless question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:23.60,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But then, why did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're moving? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man your age living in your parent's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so envious of your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You... do understand how busy the office is during this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a Christmas party, and end of the year party, a New Year's party,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and in just a few more weeks there's going to be a Valentine's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's going to be a hellish time of party planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you say you're moving tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I guess you've already found your apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anywhere in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then decide now while we're working outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there are any conditions you want, let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I believe there's enough to suit you in here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's close to the station and there's a convenience store right there, so shopping should be easy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is closer to the office than my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a very convenient apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to decide on your conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can he move in tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. If I have the deposit and take care of some paperwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then I'll be able to talk with the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paperwork as in...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the very least, the lease contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can wait for the guarantor's seal until tomorrow though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what are you gazing at by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not gazing at anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's such a stupid answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've seemed so lifeless since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that I don't really feel like going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not "fine" at all, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's play games as much as we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's listen to CDs as much as we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat snacks as much as we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we can also chit-chat as much as we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cheer up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello Nanoka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should clean this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop being so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, I will, so just be quiet, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never do it when no one tells you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Nanoka and I have something important to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a complicated issue that you'll never get, Onee.{I'll leave it up to you how you want to handle Onee. Kind of feels like we have to use it since we have Onii-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of clothing, let me borrow that blue shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.50,TL Note,,0,0,0,,fukuzatsu = complicated, fuku = clothing{Kanji are different though}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you gave it to me and would never wear it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I changed my mind now. Hand it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monster! Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're moving tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be busy with this and that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure I pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be running away in the middle of the night if it really was "nothing".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say such cynical things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what you're doing is pretty much a night flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's cheap! Loser goes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee, you're being so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person is going to become a bride next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Annual tribute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's finally going to pay her annual tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.70,TL Note,,0,0,0,,Japanese idiom for getting married
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you girls found guys yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the best time for "it".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It" meaning pure love relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that while your marriage got arranged...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just meant for relationship purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's much more to think about when it comes to marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you marry someone because you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like my fiancé, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just liking him isn't enough for this arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are various constraints in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you come to the point where you ask "is this really okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With you gone, this place will be so much more peaceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that a call from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-ah, yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-she said she's staying at a friend's house or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is the Saeki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be staying at Futaba-chan's home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad just told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I also said that I'll be back before noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think I'll stay here a bit longer, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}You know...{\i0} \N -I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{\i0}Sorry. {\i1}\N -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.85,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,You're not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About me asking what you thought about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be eating first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked you such a weird question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.35,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Ah, you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you said... I was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.45,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not weird and I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be the one apologizing for doing that to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I know it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:58.85,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I cared a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.35,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't really care that much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.35,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be able to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.55,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.55,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.95,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.25,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll call off staying over here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.05,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food's going to be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee, you eat too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, I made these myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to wear your wedding dress at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The say, "One second of negligence, one lifetime of obesity".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Not hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or does the food look nasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then eat up! It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Hey Futaba, grab some for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But man, it's not like I'm saying no to you living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know this came out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for saying this all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you not satisfied with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else you wouldn't say you want to move out all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been thinking about it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, just be sincere and tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you're not content with about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or did something happen between you and Nanoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just felt like coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you're moving out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we... sleep together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold it for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am strange... after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though we're siblings, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm saying such selfish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine because we're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stuff like this... in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why are you moving out, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's make a promise, tonight's the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like "the last time"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going somewhere that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always had something I wanted to say, but couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember when we rode on the ferris wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I wasn't really sure back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the truth is..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was very happy that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why at this rate, I...
